     В                                Notes:                              л


     л  Red Mercury - Its the world's newest nightmare: A compact 
     л  thermonuclear weapon, or "backpack nuke," that can be smuggled 
     л  virtually anywhere. As a special Shadow Ops operative, track an
     л  underground terrorist group, intent on unleashing this nightmare
     л  on the world. From crowded Middle Eastern streets to the jungles
     л  of the Congo and beyond, the chase has begun. An intense first 
     л  person shooter of incredible authenticity, intensity and 
     л  powerhouse sound, Shadow Ops: Red Mercury is the perfect blend of
     л  heart pounding interactivity and masterful Hollywood production 
     л  value.
